When you hear Bus, you think: stuffy air, no legroom, practically sitting on top of the person next to you, and just genuinely being uncomfortable… 

@thejet.coach bus is simply NOT that — it’s a first-class bus experience that combines the luxury & personal space of a private jet with the affordability & convenience of a motorcoach! There’s only 18 seats so you have PLENTY of room, the seats have motion cancelling technology, and there’s plenty of chargers, fast wifi, and FREE alcohol 💯🚌

DC (Metro Center) ↔️ NYC (Hudson Yards)

Studio Ghibli lovers rejoice because you can stay in the hotel which inspired Miyazaki’s film Spirited Away! Stepping into this Tokyo hotel will truly transport you to another world, or in other words, Yubaba’s bath house! Each room is adorned with the most intricate Japanese art which is so awe-inspiring that even my dreams couldn’t imagine such beauty. It’s easy to see why Miyazaki was so inspired by this location! 

This quickly became one of my favourite hotel stays to date and I encourage anyone visiting Tokyo to pay a visit ❤️

